zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tec1665703247413.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tec1665703247413.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tec1665703247413.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tec1665703247413\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the character set used for communication with the operating system and for communication between Uniface and non-Uniface components, if they are not Unicode-based.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tec1665703247413__topic_d143210e1_d143211e1_d143212e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tec1665703247413__p_d143213e1_d143214e1_d143215e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SYS_CHARSET</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">CharacterSet</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tec1665703247413__section_yml_w1z_kwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1219724e65\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tec1665703247413__table_d17042e1_d17043e1_d17044e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tec1665703247413__section_scr_z1z_kwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1219724e111\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tec1665703247413__p_d143222e1_d143223e1_d143224e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">CharacterSet</var>—character set\n            sup